channel.title: Anal Cunt - most epic band ever?
channel.description:
So yeah, post your favourite Anal Cunt lyrics here. I'll start:
The song name is "I Made Fun Of You Because Your Kid Just Died". [code] I was at the hospital laughing at cripples Then I heard your kid just died Suddenly, that was funnier than the cripples So I tracked you down and made fun of you
[Chorus:] Your kid died, and you cried And I thought it was funny [x2]
It was an open casket wake I spilled my beer in your kid’s coffin Your mascara ran because you were crying So I kicked your husband in the balls
[Chorus][/code]
